            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%A4%E8%81%AF%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E6%97%A5-google%E6%96%B0%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E6%81%90%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E8%A8%98%E6%86%B6%E9%AB%94-%E6%BD%98%E5%81%A5%E6%88%90%E9%A7%81-%E5%8F%8D%E8%80%8C%E5%88%BA%E6%BF%80flash%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82%E7%88%86%E6%8E%89-042839783.html",
